<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>MoviMate Landing</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e1e1e, #2b2b2b);
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .container h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .buttons {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #ff3c00;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #ff5733;
    }

    .features-heading {
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 20, 147, 1);
    }

    .features-heading span {
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 20, 147, 1);
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
      gap: 25px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      max-width: 1400px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    @media(min-width: 768px) {
      .cards {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #000000, #1a1a1a);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      box-shadow: none;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateX(8px) translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0px 20px 50px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: orange;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      object-fit: contain;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .about-section {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #111, #1c1c1c);
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffa500, #ff0080);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .about-section p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #bbb;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background-color: #111;
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .card {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1><i class="fas fa-film"></i> Welcome to <strong>MoviMate</strong></h1>
    <p><i class="fas fa-video"></i> Your intelligent movie assistant for discovering the best in cinema.</p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/login" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login</a>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h3 class="features-heading"><i class='fas fa-arrow-right' style='color: white; margin-right: 10px;'></i><span>Key Features</span></h3>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3031/3031293.png" alt="Search Engine Icon" style="filter: brightness(0) invert(1);">
        <h3>Real-Time Search</h3>
        <p>Find any movie or series instantly with intelligent, auto-complete powered search.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1055/1055687.png" alt="Fire Icon">
        <h3>ðŸ”¥ Trending & Upcoming</h3>
        <p>Explore what's buzzing in cinemas and what's set to release soon.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3135/3135715.png" alt="Cast Icon">
        <h3>Cast & Crew Insights</h3>
        <p>Access detailed profiles of actors, directors, and producers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1828/1828884.png" alt="Ratings Icon">
        <h3>Ratings & Reviews</h3>
        <p>View community ratings, professional reviews, and critic scores in one place.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/681/681611.png" alt="Poster with Paint Brush Icon">
        <h3>High-Quality Posters</h3>
        <p>Enjoy stunning poster art and stills from your favorite titles in HD.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3050/3050525.png" alt="Document Icon with Lines">
        <h3>Release Information</h3>
        <p>Stay updated with theatrical and OTT release schedules across regions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2><i class="fas fa-clapperboard" style="color: white;"></i> About MoviMate</h2>
    <p>MoviMate is your trusted companion in the cinematic universe. Whether you want to check out the latest blockbusters, explore classic gems, or discover hidden indie hits, MoviMate delivers real-time information including reviews, ratings, cast details, and eye-catching posters. Built for film enthusiasts, by film enthusiasts.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> Crafted with care by movie lovers. Dive into the world of films with <strong>MoviMate</strong> today!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
